title: cryptoyogibo
author: cryptoyogibo
content: Uroboros meme contest ends in 4 hours - win 20 BUSD and a role in DiscordGM! Less than five hours to go until the end of the meme competition. Don't miss out on the opportunity to win a role and a cash prize - 20 BUSD. By the way, owning a role greatly increases your chances of receiving rewards from the project, e.g. #airdrophttps://twitter.com/uroborosdefi/status/1578427055418400773https://preview.redd.it/0ayqdw1iuys91.png?width=800&format=png&auto=webp&s=1b7533397b397f7212126c7793e1e394fe7310e6Rewards for early community membersWe wish to form a community of people who endorse the same values and can help us build the product and participate in the life of DAO Uroboros. Therefore, we will slightly lift the veil of some planning activities:● Airdrop, designed primarily for contributors, ambassadors and active users of the project.● A co-building channel for the real web3 enthusiasts will be launched on the Discord server with the opportunity to participate in the product co-building and to be the first to test this service and provide the feedback.● A collection of NFTs will be launched, the owners of which will be able to receive benefits from transfers. OMG! Getting on the whitelist is not that easy! :-)● OG roles and fun competitions with prize funds!● Reduced payment commissions and awesome farming conditions for active users!● Access to closed functionality. Be the first to get profit from Uroboros!Join us on social networks and instant messengers — there you can learn more about our project and explore its roadmap and whitepaper. Keep your finger on the pulse! New announcements coming soon.Discord: https://discord.gg/MpTqKFxsFATwitter: https://twitter.com/uroborosdefiTelegram: https://t.me/uroborosdefi
